
flowchart LR
    S[Legacy Databases] --> P[Profiling & Assessment]
    P --> M[Source to Target Mapping]
    M --> C[Data Cleansing / Standardization]
    C --> L[Initial Historical Load]
    S --> D[CDC Capture]
    D --> R[Real-Time Replication / Sync]
    L --> T[Target Domain Database]
    R --> T
    T --> Q[Reconciliation & Validation]
    Q --> U[Parallel Run]
    U --> X[Controlled Cutover]
    X --> Z[Legacy Decommission]